== 製作 ==
2020年3月，宣佈[[馬特·貝蒂內利-奧爾平|馬特·貝蒂內利-奧爾平]]和{{le|泰勒·吉列特|Tyler Gillett}}將執導第五部《驚聲尖叫》電影，[[凱文·威廉森|凱文·威廉森]]擔任編劇和執行製片人，並已經進入正式開發階段，電影有望於2020年5月開始拍攝<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://collider.com/scream-5-ready-or-not-radio-silence-director-plot-details/|title='Scream 5' Scores 'Ready or Not' Team Radio Silence to Direct (& Scare Us Silly)|last=Gemmill|first=Allie|date=2020-03-12|website=Collider|access-date=2020-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200429191002/https://collider.com/scream-5-ready-or-not-radio-silence-director-plot-details/|archive-date=2020-04-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年5月，宣佈[[妮芙·坎貝爾|妮芙·坎貝爾]]正為回歸出演{{le|席妮·皮斯考克|Sidney Prescott}}進行洽談<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/neve-campbell-bittersweet-scream-5-talks-1294252|title=Neve Campbell on 'Castle in the Ground' and Bittersweet 'Scream 5' Talks|website=The Hollywood Reporter|first=Brian|last=Davids|date=2020-05-11|accessdate=2020-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200516022035/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/neve-campbell-bittersweet-scream-5-talks-1294252|archive-date=2020-05-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同月，宣佈[[大衛·艾奎特|大衛·艾奎特]]回歸飾演杜威·瑞利，[[詹姆斯·范德比爾特|詹姆斯·范德比爾特]]和蓋·布西克擔任編劇，並將於本年晚些時候在[[北卡羅萊納州|北卡羅萊納州]]的[[威明頓_(北卡羅來納州)|威明頓]]進行拍攝<ref>{{cite web|url=https://indiemacuser.co.uk/2020/05/18/david-arquette-will-return-in-scream-reboot/|title=David Arquette Will Return In Scream 5|website=Indie Mac User|date=2020-05-18|accessdate=2020-09-22}}</ref>。2020年6月，據《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》報導，該片將由[[派拉蒙影業|派拉蒙影業]]發行，並計劃於2021年上映<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|last=Kroll|first=Justin|last2=Kroll|first2=Justin|date=2020-06-24|title=New ‘Scream’ Movie From Spyglass Media Will Be Released by Paramount (EXCLUSIVE)|url=https://variety.com/2020/film/news/paramount-and-spyglass-scream-1234648119/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200624205349/https://variety.com/2020/film/news/paramount-and-spyglass-scream-1234648119/|archive-date=2020-06-24|access-date=2020-06-24|website=Variety}}</ref>。2020年7月底，確認[[寇特妮·考克絲|寇特妮·考克絲]]回歸飾演{{le|蓋兒·魏德斯|Gale Weathers}}<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|date=2020-07-31|title=‘Scream’: Courteney Cox Reprising Her Role As News Reporter Gale Weathers In Spyglass Media Group & Paramount Relaunch|url=https://deadline.com/2020/07/courteney-cox-joins-scream-sequel-paramount-spyglass-1203000820/|access-date=2020-07-31|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|archive-date=2020-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731174431/https://deadline.com/2020/07/courteney-cox-joins-scream-sequel-paramount-spyglass-1203000820/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年8月，{{le|梅莉莎·巴雷拉|Melissa Barrera (actress)}}和[[珍娜·奧特嘉|珍娜·奧特嘉]]加盟劇組<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/08/scream-vida-star-melissa-barrera-joins-courteney-cox-movie-spyglass-media-group-paramount-1203015161/|title=‘Scream’: ‘Vida’ & ‘In The Heights’ Star Melissa Barrera Set For Key Role In Spyglass & Paramount Slasher Movie Relaunch|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|first=Andreas|last=Wiseman|date=2020-08-17|accessdate=2020-08-17}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/08/scream-jenna-ortega-joins-spyglass-media-group-paramount-pictures-horror-relaunch-1203017853/|title=‘Scream’: Jenna Ortega Joins Spyglass Media Group & Paramount Pictures’ Horror Relaunch|website=Deadline Hollywood|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|date=2020-08-19|accessdate=2020-08-19|archive-date=2020-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819221821/https://deadline.com/2020/08/scream-jenna-ortega-joins-spyglass-media-group-paramount-pictures-horror-relaunch-1203017853/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年9月，[[傑克·奎德|傑克·奎德]]、{{le|梅森·古丁|Mason Gooding}}、[[迪倫·明奈特|迪倫·明奈特]]、[[凱爾·加納|凱爾·加納]]、{{le|潔絲敏·莎懷·布朗|Jasmin Savoy Brown}}以及{{le|蜜琪·麥迪遜|Mikey Madison}}加盟劇組，而[[瑪莉·雪登|瑪莉·雪登]]回歸飾演茱蒂·希克斯<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/09/jack-quaid-paramount-spyglass-new-scream-1203028527/|title=‘Scream’: Jack Quaid To Star in Spyglass Media Group and Paramount’s Horror Relaunch|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|first=Justin|last=Kroll|date=2020-09-01|accessdate=2020-09-01|archive-date=2020-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200901221941/https://deadline.com/2020/09/jack-quaid-paramount-spyglass-new-scream-1203028527/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/09/love-victors-mason-gooding-dylan-minnette-scream-movie-1234574582/|title=Mason Gooding And Dylan Minnette Join Ensemble Of New ‘Scream’ Movie|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|first=Justin|last=Kroll|date=2020-09-10|accessdate=2020-09-10|archive-date=2020-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200910213853/https://deadline.com/2020/09/love-victors-mason-gooding-dylan-minnette-scream-movie-1234574582/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同月，宣佈[[妮芙·坎貝爾|妮芙·坎貝爾]]回歸飾演{{le|席妮·皮斯考克|Sidney Prescott}}<ref>{{Cite web|last=Vary|first=Adam B.|last2=Vary|first2=Adam B.|date=2020-09-10|title=Neve Campbell Returning to ‘Scream’ Franchise as Sidney Prescott|url=https://variety.com/2020/film/news/neve-campbell-scream-relaunch-sidney-prescott-1234765712/|access-date=2020-09-10|website=Variety|archive-date=2020-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200910210914/https://variety.com/2020/film/news/neve-campbell-scream-relaunch-sidney-prescott-1234765712/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而[[索妮雅·阿瑪|索妮雅·阿瑪]]加盟劇組<ref name=":2">{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2020/film/global/sonia-ammar-joins-cast-of-scream-5-set-to-start-shooting-later-this-month-exclusive-1234773213/|title=Sonia Ammar Joins Cast of ‘Scream 5,’ Set to Start Shooting Later This Month (EXCLUSIVE)|website=Variety|first=Elsa|last=Keslassy|date=2020-09-17|accessdate=2020-09-17|archive-date=2020-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920184209/https://variety.com/2020/film/global/sonia-ammar-joins-cast-of-scream-5-set-to-start-shooting-later-this-month-exclusive-1234773213/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 拍攝 ===
